{"tid":1575020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大學生會會長被打壓到辭咗職啦呀!!!文宣呀!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:33:31.000Z","uid":199727,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f817be01378124532b7387b93de83024c8adfff","tid":1575020,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"呢單野一定要重視，否則下一屆大專學生會就無人敢出黎選!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會署理會長黃程鋒辭職 辭職信稱上月底遇襲 考慮家人自身安全已離港<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wong_cCZ2s_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwong_cCZ2s_1200x0.png&h=535bdbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港大學學生會署理會長黃程鋒，今日去信港大學生評議會，辭去署理會長職務。據他的辭職信指，他在 8 月 30 日在灣仔遇襲，考慮家人和自身安全後決定辭職，形容辭去學生會職務是他最大的遺憾，形容今次離港是「單程旅途（one way trip）」，亦是他「畢生的恥辱（lifelong shame）」但他相信，「不久的將來我會回來（And I believe, one day and very soon, I will be back.）」。<br />\n<br />\n黃程鋒在辭職信指，他在 8 月 30 日凌晨在灣仔被白衣人用藤條襲擊，他相信襲擊是有計劃有組織，在他遇襲的 24 小時內，民陣召集人岑子杰和元朗遊行申請人鍾健平亦遇襲，包括港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐等 28 名社運領袖被捕，反映經過多月的抗爭，政府未有向人民負責，反而透過種種手段打壓抗爭和學生。<br />\n<br />\n他形容不會原諒自己在關鍵時刻離開香港，是他畢生的恥辱，但他亦要顧及家人，過去數月他們面對很大的壓力以至危險，所以最終他決定離開，和學生會其他成員商討後，認為他不能繼續履行署理會長職務所以決定辭職。黃程鋒又指即使身在海外，他的抗爭亦不會結束，這場運動是良知、人性和尊嚴與極權的戰鬥，將會寫入列冊，「願榮光歸香港（Glory to Hong Kong）」。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%BD%B2%E7%90%86%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E9%BB%83%E7%A8%8B%E9%8B%92%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E4%BF%A1%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25A8%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7-%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86reNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=77c3680c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25A8%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7-%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&h=f3ca7262\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%BD%B2%E7%90%86%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E9%BB%83%E7%A8%8B%E9%8B%92%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E4%BF%A1%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF/</a>"},{"pid":"219ea1858c5ba13ffa1729ae5c2ea4cf9618e35a","tid":1575020,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7ba2c757c0d1eb4973348f58f2c8a7d106ff642","tid":1575020,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"829c82c517783438507c6b7b26d775c3fb880efb","tid":1575020,"uid":76366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05ba2d70d9df4f5974e0d92424b49b20dfc29d2d","tid":1575020,"uid":301560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:14:42.000Z","m